    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### Asignar la media de precios a los precios de venta nulos 💵💵💵💵\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "eyBoLGn8muhH"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Media de precio de venta total\n",
        "df['precio_venta'].fillna(df['precio_venta'].mean(), inplace=True)\n",
